entries.journal_entry_description: Nawika mentioned her lost jewelry box. She only remembers visiting her husband in the crystal garden right outside the village. She suspects it could be found there. It would be wise, however, to extend your search further. Check out the entrance to the Deep Depths just in case.
entries.task00_journal_entry_description: Find Nawika's Jewelry box. Look in the Crystal Gardens and the entrance to the Deep Depths.
entries.task01_journal_entry_description: Find Nawika's Necklace and bring it back to her.
